script:
1). You wouldn't happen to have change for a dollar, would you?
Yes, I believe I do. Here you are. 
Sorry, I have change for a dollar.
No I didn't. Sorry about that.
2). Mr. Roth is here to see you.
Good to see you too.
She will come tomorrow.
Please send him in. 
3). Why don't we call it a day?
Oh, I didn't know.
Good idea. I'm tired. 
Why don't you call him?
